@c ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@node nextafter, math
@findex nextafter
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <math.h>

double nextafter(double x, double y);
@end example

@subheading Description

@code{nextafter} determines the next representable value after @var{x} in
the direction of @var{y}.

@subheading Return Value

@code{nextafter} returns @var{x} incremented in the direction of @var{y}.

@subheading Portability

@portability ansi, posix
